# Title: Equation Group DLL_U Export Function Load
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2019-03-04
# Level: critical
# Description: Detects a specific export function name used by one of EquationGroup tools
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.g0020, attack.t1218.011, detection.emerging-threats
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules-emerging-threats/2019/TA/EquationGroup/proc_creation_win_apt_equationgroup_dll_u_load.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Unlikely

CommandLine="*-export dll_u*" OR CommandLine IN ("*,dll_u", "* dll_u")